723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:42:10.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"3b2c7528e679aab2fab03db162a226a1f40b1d3c","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:42:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16333326dd198d059c3e261e1eb3872c70e14cd0","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b81668f2d71783bf83ca5b6732d304a2bf3292b","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf49b22e082d1b0774b022e39f4c5960aa2d1f61","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:54:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd7cca7639270e29117860e8318dbf51aefe6cb4","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:54:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"911af2d095bb50e3d8964ff1cedb55e9f7a3041a","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf313dae03fc64b7468e42d23ab71484a61eeb05","tid":1723558,"uid":41344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f323d321539bbef8fd84915f73695542a43d4e26","tid":1723558,"uid":75718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0e43f71b31da3d61c56a85edacb107ddb7f8b67","tid":1723558,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"有道理, 但唔易做<br />\n更重要係現代人可以出街食<br />\n當然, 可以試, 各有各做, no harm"},{"pid":"b3e71cd8750142b77a787a19612db1ea67ab6ca6","tid":1723558,"uid":218729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7726067e296f2dc37f4a5e9f0708a7d6ec392be","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一. 中共陽謀</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JBhZUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JBhZUF.jpg&h=4a95a5fa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉教授話齋：「某方劇本已經好清晰。」（註一）中共既陽謀正係佢既拿手好戲：<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾鬥群眾</span>。有時候手足裝修set rb，咁耐都唔見PoPo出黎（其實要出真係好快），一黎係港共將鄉黑利益同自己綑綁，以及煽動藍絲廢老自發去斬人，二黎係等班只係顧住搵食既港豬覺得「社會冇秩序、冇左警察唔掂」（見良心警接受韓媒訪問）。可見港共政權今後都會沿用呢個策略，元朗7.21、荃灣斬人、尋日上水鄉黑出動，只係早於黎明前黑暗既灰暗，今後鄉黑手段會越黎越心狠手辣。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，目前最大威力既揸春袋&mdash;「<span style=\"color: blue;\">強迫三罷</span>」，只係成功咗一半（都冇）。九龍、港島交通順到呢，一堆人照樣番工呀大佬！(註三)呢兩日晨早6點幾排長龍來回屋企（九龍半島）同新界北&amp;東，小巴上面有邊啲人唔係屌梗我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到粉嶺、大埔旁聽街坊講野，一直猛咁鬧班靚仔。受三罷影響最大係新界東居民，封咗吐露港之後既新界東儼如與世隔絕。繼續現況只會白白失去呢一帶居心既支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">絕對唔係分化撚反裝修反rb反三罷，睇埋落去先。</span><br />\n<br />\n假設你保到民心，戰況都唔可以膠著落去。中共老謀心算，一早實行梗「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留島不留人</span></strong></span>」政策，全香港人、鄉黑同popo會係毒煙底下一齊攬炒。好似黃偉豪教授所言「現在的警隊就是當時在西藏揮舞日本刀，負責『止暴制亂』的蒙古騎兵，但到頭來，盲目效忠換來的是被徹底清算的悲慘下場。」（註二）攬炒既目的係要支爆，而唔係自爆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">呢加場抗爭已經去到一個兩難之局：<br />\nA. 繼續set rb搞（半成功）既三罷，結果失民心同吸毒煙死；<br />\nB. 武力升級（又升唔到）而部份小隊轉向更極端既手段，結果又係失民心同PoPo有藉口更凶殘對待手足。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二. 和理非最終升級：<span style=\"color: red;\">「和理掃」</span></span></span><br />\n咁到底罷定唔罷？我發覺我地既想法僵化咗，一直只係透過警暴去爭取民心；因為我地係打擾居民既一方，從冇大膽假設過我方喺安定社會方面可以取代政府既功能。<br />\n<br />\n新思路方向：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如何經濟攬炒而不失民心、甚至令民心轉向？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我朋友個腦海諗起朱元璋建國方針：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">「高築牆，廣積糧，緩稱王」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(冇錯，暴大、理大、城大既手足已經慢慢完成梗「高築牆」既條件，我會代朋友係另一個post再講。)</span><br />\n呢個post重點係「廣積糧」。點做？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內容：一句講哂。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非狂<strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">掃</span></ins></strong>同囤積上水、粉嶺、太和、大埔墟四區<span style=\"color: green;\">最平</span>兼<span style=\"color: orange;\">最基本</span>既糧食，<span style=\"color: red;\">做良好市民刺激消費</span>，然後等當地糧食短缺，再由手足／手足＋區議會參選人進場向廣大市民派發物資</span><br />\n時間：可唔可以11月20號、11月21號、11月22號既早上9點？<br />\n地點：上水、粉嶺、太和、大埔墟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的係乜？</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: blue;\">會製造恐慌效果嫁</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好啊！</span><br />\n強迫「三罷」本來係令班港豬發覺已經唔到佢地置身事外，但喺糧食充裕既情況底下，佢地點會覺得恐慌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「三罷」之所以未竟全功，就係欠咗令物資短缺呢一步。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: blue;\">拉攏民心</span><br />\n你會問：<em>會唔會掃唔哂啲貨？</em><br />\n重點：所以要揀<ins>最平</ins>既掃，最平既冇哂，市民就<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唯有買比較貴既食物</span>，到時手足免費派發，仲唔贏盡民心？俾中立、淺藍港豬以及阿公阿婆知道手足唔係暴徒。更重要既係削弱佢地心裡認為政府係合法(legitimate)管治者既基礎，原來令佢地生活安定既係可以有另一班人。1995年阪神大地震，就係黑社會山口組第一時間派發物資。（「從戰後一直到阪神大地震，每當混亂期，山口組的動作總是比法制內的警察和政府機關還快，神戶市民全看在眼中。也因此今年的山口組「萬聖節活動」，絕大部分的神戶市民都表示歡迎。」）(註四)<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（我朋友只係學術討論梗合法性問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，詳見Max Weber既<em>Politics as a Vocation</em>）</span><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: blue;\">有助區議會選情(短期)</span><br />\n班建制狗咪又係靠派鹽派米攞盡民意？我地呢加做同樣既野唔得？（麻煩法律、選舉巴絲fact check咁樣會唔會違反啲乜野選舉規。違反左既話，手足派既時候記得同公公婆婆講唔好投邊啲建制狗）<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: blue;\">我地正處於內戰邊緣</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(This is 客觀分析，冇鼓吹)</span><br />\n屋企儲糧食俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，餓死對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，兼且部份野其實係戰略物資（見「掃貨清單」）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>點解揀上述四區？</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. 講咗，以上四區民心逐漸喪失，要諗辦法爭取番。而且根據我實地考察，封吐露港之後，呢兩日以上四區的確出現物資短缺既現象（見圖），而我聽到有街坊已經傳梗物資唔夠，開始驚而買定物資。係呢幾區做，絕對係火上加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfWqpxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfWqpxX.jpg&h=0e6d3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 本來以上四區既交通已經擁擠，配合<span style=\"color: brown;\">「和理塞」</span>行動，人地真係返唔到工嫁，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好阿</span></span>！你仲要趁啲港豬返工搶哂啲食糧，港豬放工番屋企肚餓點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 全港一齊做唔夠集中，起唔到效果。<br />\n4. 射波俾POPO，最終令市民相信係PoPo封左吐露港引致。（請文宣組睇「文宣部份」）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「掃貨清單」</span></strong></ins><br />\n建議以下物品：<br />\n1. 所有穀物類食品：米、杯麵、任何麵條<br />\n2. 罐頭<br />\n3. 牛奶<br />\n4. 雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n原因:<br />\n一. 牛奶同雞蛋。過左期好<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭</span></span></ins></strong>呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二. 罐頭。高空擲物容易<ins>誤中狗隻</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，切勿以身試法。<br />\n三. 穀物類食品同罐頭存放期耐，方便日後派發，派剩又冇浪費。<br />\n四. 再多就真係怕冇效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>文宣部份</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔需要將以上目的講明</span></ins></strong>，避免民怨燒到去示威者身上。等中立同淺藍港豬不明所以，只係見到物資短缺，以為香港出事。我絕對expect深藍會話係呢場運動造成，但佢地唔係target，無需要理會。<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暗黑宣傳</span></span></strong>：叫大家諗下，其實會唔會係政府打算餓死中大學生，妄顧北區、大埔區居民生計，將吐露港封死？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「和理掃」與各行動關係</span></strong></ins><br />\n大家可能覺得呢加做既野毫無目標，但「和理掃」就係要每一個行動都必需要配合先可以成功:<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span>RB、「和理塞」配合「和理掃」，會癱瘓北區、大埔路面糧食運輸。<br />\n2. 根據理由(1)，<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴大必守</span></span></strong></ins>。(但尊重學生，學生係最終決定者。「暴大係全香港人既」同「香港係全中國人既」無撚分別。)<br />\n3. 分分鐘對家會賣糧食，唔可以刺激對家消售。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以&hellip;? 明就明。<br />\n4. 繼續「三罷」。「和理掃」同「三罷」係互相配合，令大家逐漸醒覺呢加發生緊乜野事，同埋。<br />\n<br />\n「和理掃」係令各行動結合，<ins>賦予左每一個行動意義</ins>，我地既運動絕對未去到漫無方向既地步。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「和理掃」大戰略</span></strong></ins><br />\n「和理掃」係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">經濟版</span>既<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>赤壁之戰</strong></span></span>。此計一成，盡收新界東民心入吾等彀中，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴大即荊州</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天下二分可矣</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QldOqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QldOqA&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=add97dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QldOqA</a> <br />\n註二: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2q2jQBX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2q2jQBX&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=0fa3261c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2q2jQBX</a><br />\n註三: 有大數據分析(<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34Xrqwi \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34Xrqwi%20&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=894dff96\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34Xrqwi </a>) 話民心冇影響，但個「大」數據只收集連登同香討意見，好圍爐。<br />\n註四: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2CIVXSv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2CIVXSv&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=75b445f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2CIVXSv</a><br />\n<br />\n(其實「和理掃」既idea出現之後，其他人掃而你唔掃既話，最終蝕底既係你。偷偷底話你知，我個frd尋日已經係大埔墟買左10盒雞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，到時候你連炒蛋都冇得食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d21196b5decc159380a91b352113e81d139e7dbe","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0e43f71b31da3d61c56a85edacb107ddb7f8b67","tid":1723558,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:11:19.000Z","msg":"有道理, 但唔易做<br />\n更重要係現代人可以出街食<br />\n當然, 可以試, 各有各做, no harm"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:28:45.000Z","msg":"的確唔易做<br />\n重要條件「再塞吐露港」好似已經唔得了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有關出街食呢個問題，我都諗過。如果掃貨成功，最後效果可能會係推高中立基層既生活成本，我覺得令佢地驚驚地，又唔係真係太影響，其實已經可以搶到民心了。<br />\n<br />\n更好既係食肆都冇貨，大前日我個frd去大埔墟大家樂食早餐，連通粉都賣哂。"},{"pid":"7d2b382d112de893ac333cd218dcccc48aee342f","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"911af2d095bb50e3d8964ff1cedb55e9f7a3041a","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:55:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:29:42.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄猛推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9eb4761a7f3933dceb6fc58b973a7e1496d68f6","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:32:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11a9ba15d5fcba26b14b01e979985ef83b755b89","tid":1723558,"uid":147784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"005407e42654d08eed8148175581918a5b881446","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f323d321539bbef8fd84915f73695542a43d4e26","tid":1723558,"uid":75718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:05:43.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9d1c9ba6189e548c791704e12550e02830f5e09","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3e71cd8750142b77a787a19612db1ea67ab6ca6","tid":1723558,"uid":218729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7726067e296f2dc37f4a5e9f0708a7d6ec392be","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:27:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一. 中共陽謀</span></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3JBhZUF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3JBhZUF.jpg&h=4a95a5fa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n沈旭暉教授話齋：「某方劇本已經好清晰。」（註一）中共既陽謀正係佢既拿手好戲：<span style=\"color: red;\">群眾鬥群眾</span>。有時候手足裝修set rb，咁耐都唔見PoPo出黎（其實要出真係好快），一黎係港共將鄉黑利益同自己綑綁，以及煽動藍絲廢老自發去斬人，二黎係等班只係顧住搵食既港豬覺得「社會冇秩序、冇左警察唔掂」（見良心警接受韓媒訪問）。可見港共政權今後都會沿用呢個策略，元朗7.21、荃灣斬人、尋日上水鄉黑出動，只係早於黎明前黑暗既灰暗，今後鄉黑手段會越黎越心狠手辣。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，目前最大威力既揸春袋&mdash;「<span style=\"color: blue;\">強迫三罷</span>」，只係成功咗一半（都冇）。九龍、港島交通順到呢，一堆人照樣番工呀大佬！(註三)呢兩日晨早6點幾排長龍來回屋企（九龍半島）同新界北&amp;東，小巴上面有邊啲人唔係屌梗我地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />去到粉嶺、大埔旁聽街坊講野，一直猛咁鬧班靚仔。受三罷影響最大係新界東居民，封咗吐露港之後既新界東儼如與世隔絕。繼續現況只會白白失去呢一帶居心既支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">絕對唔係分化撚反裝修反rb反三罷，睇埋落去先。</span><br />\n<br />\n假設你保到民心，戰況都唔可以膠著落去。中共老謀心算，一早實行梗「<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">留島不留人</span></strong></span>」政策，全香港人、鄉黑同popo會係毒煙底下一齊攬炒。好似黃偉豪教授所言「現在的警隊就是當時在西藏揮舞日本刀，負責『止暴制亂』的蒙古騎兵，但到頭來，盲目效忠換來的是被徹底清算的悲慘下場。」（註二）攬炒既目的係要支爆，而唔係自爆。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">呢加場抗爭已經去到一個兩難之局：<br />\nA. 繼續set rb搞（半成功）既三罷，結果失民心同吸毒煙死；<br />\nB. 武力升級（又升唔到）而部份小隊轉向更極端既手段，結果又係失民心同PoPo有藉口更凶殘對待手足。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">二. 和理非最終升級：<span style=\"color: red;\">「和理掃」</span></span></span><br />\n咁到底罷定唔罷？我發覺我地既想法僵化咗，一直只係透過警暴去爭取民心；因為我地係打擾居民既一方，從冇大膽假設過我方喺安定社會方面可以取代政府既功能。<br />\n<br />\n新思路方向：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如何經濟攬炒而不失民心、甚至令民心轉向？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n呢個時候我朋友個腦海諗起朱元璋建國方針：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">「高築牆，廣積糧，緩稱王」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">(冇錯，暴大、理大、城大既手足已經慢慢完成梗「高築牆」既條件，我會代朋友係另一個post再講。)</span><br />\n呢個post重點係「廣積糧」。點做？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內容：一句講哂。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理非狂<strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">掃</span></ins></strong>同囤積上水、粉嶺、太和、大埔墟四區<span style=\"color: green;\">最平</span>兼<span style=\"color: orange;\">最基本</span>既糧食，<span style=\"color: red;\">做良好市民刺激消費</span>，然後等當地糧食短缺，再由手足／手足＋區議會參選人進場向廣大市民派發物資</span><br />\n時間：可唔可以11月20號、11月21號、11月22號既早上9點？<br />\n地點：上水、粉嶺、太和、大埔墟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">目的係乜？</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. <span style=\"color: blue;\">會製造恐慌效果嫁</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好啊！</span><br />\n強迫「三罷」本來係令班港豬發覺已經唔到佢地置身事外，但喺糧食充裕既情況底下，佢地點會覺得恐慌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「三罷」之所以未竟全功，就係欠咗令物資短缺呢一步。<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: blue;\">拉攏民心</span><br />\n你會問：<em>會唔會掃唔哂啲貨？</em><br />\n重點：所以要揀<ins>最平</ins>既掃，最平既冇哂，市民就<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">唯有買比較貴既食物</span>，到時手足免費派發，仲唔贏盡民心？俾中立、淺藍港豬以及阿公阿婆知道手足唔係暴徒。更重要既係削弱佢地心裡認為政府係合法(legitimate)管治者既基礎，原來令佢地生活安定既係可以有另一班人。1995年阪神大地震，就係黑社會山口組第一時間派發物資。（「從戰後一直到阪神大地震，每當混亂期，山口組的動作總是比法制內的警察和政府機關還快，神戶市民全看在眼中。也因此今年的山口組「萬聖節活動」，絕大部分的神戶市民都表示歡迎。」）(註四)<span style=\"font-size: small;\">（我朋友只係學術討論梗合法性問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，詳見Max Weber既<em>Politics as a Vocation</em>）</span><br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: blue;\">有助區議會選情(短期)</span><br />\n班建制狗咪又係靠派鹽派米攞盡民意？我地呢加做同樣既野唔得？（麻煩法律、選舉巴絲fact check咁樣會唔會違反啲乜野選舉規。違反左既話，手足派既時候記得同公公婆婆講唔好投邊啲建制狗）<br />\n<br />\n4. <span style=\"color: blue;\">我地正處於內戰邊緣</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">(This is 客觀分析，冇鼓吹)</span><br />\n屋企儲糧食俾自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，餓死對家<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，兼且部份野其實係戰略物資（見「掃貨清單」）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>點解揀上述四區？</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. 講咗，以上四區民心逐漸喪失，要諗辦法爭取番。而且根據我實地考察，封吐露港之後，呢兩日以上四區的確出現物資短缺既現象（見圖），而我聽到有街坊已經傳梗物資唔夠，開始驚而買定物資。係呢幾區做，絕對係火上加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfWqpxX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfWqpxX.jpg&h=0e6d3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 本來以上四區既交通已經擁擠，配合<span style=\"color: brown;\">「和理塞」</span>行動，人地真係返唔到工嫁，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好阿</span></span>！你仲要趁啲港豬返工搶哂啲食糧，港豬放工番屋企肚餓點算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 全港一齊做唔夠集中，起唔到效果。<br />\n4. 射波俾POPO，最終令市民相信係PoPo封左吐露港引致。（請文宣組睇「文宣部份」）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「掃貨清單」</span></strong></ins><br />\n建議以下物品：<br />\n1. 所有穀物類食品：米、杯麵、任何麵條<br />\n2. 罐頭<br />\n3. 牛奶<br />\n4. 雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n原因:<br />\n一. 牛奶同雞蛋。過左期好<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">臭</span></span></ins></strong>呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二. 罐頭。高空擲物容易<ins>誤中狗隻</ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，切勿以身試法。<br />\n三. 穀物類食品同罐頭存放期耐，方便日後派發，派剩又冇浪費。<br />\n四. 再多就真係怕冇效果。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>文宣部份</span></strong></ins><br />\n1. <strong><ins><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔需要將以上目的講明</span></ins></strong>，避免民怨燒到去示威者身上。等中立同淺藍港豬不明所以，只係見到物資短缺，以為香港出事。我絕對expect深藍會話係呢場運動造成，但佢地唔係target，無需要理會。<br />\n2. <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">暗黑宣傳</span></span></strong>：叫大家諗下，其實會唔會係政府打算餓死中大學生，妄顧北區、大埔區居民生計，將吐露港封死？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「和理掃」與各行動關係</span></strong></ins><br />\n大家可能覺得呢加做既野毫無目標，但「和理掃」就係要每一個行動都必需要配合先可以成功:<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好</span>RB、「和理塞」配合「和理掃」，會癱瘓北區、大埔路面糧食運輸。<br />\n2. 根據理由(1)，<ins><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">暴大必守</span></span></strong></ins>。(但尊重學生，學生係最終決定者。「暴大係全香港人既」同「香港係全中國人既」無撚分別。)<br />\n3. 分分鐘對家會賣糧食，唔可以刺激對家消售。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以&hellip;? 明就明。<br />\n4. 繼續「三罷」。「和理掃」同「三罷」係互相配合，令大家逐漸醒覺呢加發生緊乜野事，同埋。<br />\n<br />\n「和理掃」係令各行動結合，<ins>賦予左每一個行動意義</ins>，我地既運動絕對未去到漫無方向既地步。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>「和理掃」大戰略</span></strong></ins><br />\n「和理掃」係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">經濟版</span>既<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>赤壁之戰</strong></span></span>。此計一成，盡收新界東民心入吾等彀中，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暴大即荊州</span></span>，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天下二分可矣</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n註一: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2QldOqA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2QldOqA&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=add97dd9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2QldOqA</a> <br />\n註二: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2q2jQBX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2q2jQBX&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=0fa3261c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2q2jQBX</a><br />\n註三: 有大數據分析(<a href=\"https://bit.ly/34Xrqwi \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F34Xrqwi%20&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=894dff96\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/34Xrqwi </a>) 話民心冇影響，但個「大」數據只收集連登同香討意見，好圍爐。<br />\n註四: <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2CIVXSv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2CIVXSv&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYXO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=75b445f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2CIVXSv</a><br />\n<br />\n(其實「和理掃」既idea出現之後，其他人掃而你唔掃既話，最終蝕底既係你。偷偷底話你知，我個frd尋日已經係大埔墟買左10盒雞蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，到時候你連炒蛋都冇得食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:33:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb450364d4ae79ca5254071b3b007f116a1bc6da","tid":1723558,"uid":197258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"蛇齋餅糉行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38027c26ae346d5017ff2736333b01e1a29690d6","tid":1723558,"uid":339796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb450364d4ae79ca5254071b3b007f116a1bc6da","tid":1723558,"uid":197258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:34:34.000Z","msg":"蛇齋餅糉行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:35:24.000Z","msg":"我地都搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559d890bb8de205831b2c8db827d0ac2c4899714","tid":1723558,"uid":131326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:35:39.000Z","msg":"黑警毅進狗，死全家，落地獄，大家唔洗驚照出照上街照做野，成班垃圾聲大大濫捕就叻，大家唔洗驚班狗無料到，拉完聲大大最後死狗咁放返，我打狗放火食警嫂，生勾勾，屌狗大大聲<br />\n<br />\n真。香港人，反抗，屌狗打狗"},{"pid":"4a24b6002dbb9d4ff429c1e3846